(126, 'NSIC Infrastructure', '<div style=\"padding:40px\"><div class=\"easy-breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"easy-breadcrumb_segment easy-breadcrumb_segment-front\">Home</a><span class=\"easy-breadcrumb_segment-separator\"> â€ºâ€º </span><a href=\"service.php?id=20\">\"Registration and Scheme For NSIC\"</a></div><br>\r\n<b class=\"format\">\r\n           <center> <h2>NSIC Infrastructure</h2></center>\r\n        </b>\r\n <p>To provide impetus to the marketing efforts of MSMEs, NSIC has constructed Integrated Marketing Development Centre (IMDC). The project has been envisaged keeping in view the growing demand for strategically located space to cater to the commercial & marketing needs of MSMEs/IT/ITeS etc. the building is located in the prime location of Mancheswar Industrial Estate, Bhubaneswar having excellent connectivity through road, rail and air.</p>  \r\n\r\n     <p class=\"format\"><b>Salient Features:</b></p>\r\n          <ul>\r\n<li>Ground + 7 storied building with basement having built-up area of approx.1,08,600 sq.ft.</li>\r\n<li>A truly green building designed to achieve minimum 3 star Green Rating for Integrated Habitat Assessment (GRIHA) with provision of solar street light and roof top solar power generating system.</li>\r\n<li>RCC framed structure with structural glazing and stone cladding on all faces.</li>\r\n<li>Earthquake resistance structure</li>\r\n<li>Pleasing lush green landscape all around the building.</li> \r\n<li>Ample parking space in basement, stilt and open parking around the building.</li>\r\n<li>2 nos. High Speed lifts & 100% power back up facilities.</li>\r\n<li>Latest fire detection, fire alarm and fire fighting system.</li>\r\n<li>PA System & CCTV System for security surveillance.</li>\r\n<li>VRF Air-Conditioning System.</li>\r\n<li>Large column free office space with toughened glass door.</li>\r\n<li>Separate toilets on each floor with provision of entry ramp at ground floor for the convenience.</li> \r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"format\"><b>Present Status:</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The construction of the building has been completed and booking of space is underway on first come first serve basis.</li>\r\n<li>Office space is available for leasing out to Micro, Small & Medium Enterprises, IT/ ITES units, Banks/ Financial Institutions etc.</li>\r\n<li>Interested parties may contact us at the following address for booking of space:</li> \r\n\r\n                                        <br />\r\n                                        <br />\r\n                                        <p class=\"text-center\">\r\n                                            Chief General Manager SG (Works & Estate), NSIC Ltd.,<br />\r\n                                            NSIC Bhawan, Okhla Industrial Estate,<br />\r\n                                            New Delhi- 110 020<br />\r\n                                            Telefax : (011)-26920911, 9999984250<br />\r\n                                            E-mail : <a href=\"mailto:navinchopra[at]nsic[dot]co[dot]in</a>\r\n                                        </p>\r\n                                        <br />\r\n                                        <p class=\"text-center\">\r\n                                            Integrated Marketing Development Centre (IMDC),<br />\r\n                                            IDCO Plot No. 6, Mancheswar Industrial Estate,<br />\r\n                                            Bhubaneswar,<br />\r\n                                            Mob. No. 9437022789, 7749081234<br />\r\n                                            \r\n                                            Email: <a href=\"mailto:Email: imdcbbsr[at]nsic[dot]co[dot]in\"></a>\r\n                                        </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n			   <table class=\"end\">\r\n                                    <thead>\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <th>Description</th>\r\n                                            <th>File</th>\r\n                                        </tr>\r\n                                    </thead>\r\n                                    <tbody>\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td>Brochure</td>\r\n                                            <td><a href=\"https://www.nsic.co.in/pdfs/faqinfra012017.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-xs btn-outline btn-primary\"><i class=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\"></i>&nbsp;View</a></td>\r\n                                        </tr>\r\n                                    </tbody>\r\n                                </table>\r\n\r\n		\r\n		<style>\r\n .format{\r\n	 text-align: justify;\r\n	 margin-right:20px;\r\n	 font-size:20px; font-family:Times New Roman;\r\n	 padding:10px;\r\n }\r\n </style>\r\n <br>\r\n <br>\r\n</DIV>', 126, 'INFRA', 'INFRA', 'NULL', b'1', 10, '2020-08-17 08:42:34', '2020-08-24 07:19:12'),
(127, '	Skill Development & Services', '<div style=\"padding:40px\"><div class=\"easy-breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"easy-breadcrumb_segment easy-breadcrumb_segment-front\">Home</a><span class=\"easy-breadcrumb_segment-separator\"> â€ºâ€º </span><a href=\"service.php?id=20\">\"Registration and Scheme For NSIC\"</a></div><br>\r\n<b class=\"format\">\r\n           <center> <h2>Skill Development & Services</h2></center>\r\n        </b>\r\n		<p>NSIC provides technical support to MSMEs through \'NSIC Technical Services Centres\' (NTSCs) and a number of TICs & LBIs spread across the country. The range of technical services provided through these centres include skill development in Hi-Tech as well as conventional trades, material and product testing at our testing laboratories accredited by NABL / BIS, common facilities, energy audit, environment management etc.</p>\r\n			<table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th colspan=\"2\">Description</th>\r\n                        <th>File</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td colspan=\"2\">Frequently Asked Question (FAQs)</td>\r\n                        <td><a href=\"https://www.nsic.co.in/pdfs/FAQNTSC102016.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-xs btn-outline btn-primary\"><i class=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\"></i>&nbsp;View</a></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		<style>\r\n .format{\r\n	 text-align: justify;\r\n	 margin-right:20px;\r\n	 font-size:20px; font-family:Times New Roman;\r\n	 padding:10px;\r\n }\r\n </style>\r\n <br>\r\n <br></div>\r\n', 127, 'skill', 'development', 'null', b'1', 11, '2020-08-17 08:42:34', '2020-10-20 12:06:39'),
